race.comment: UNA KNOWS (2) is mixing form and out of the placings last time but was a Mix 5 winner three starts ago and moves to Box 2 this time where she has performed well. Look for sharp improvement here. BRIGHT SIDE (5) goes very well this course and distance starting nine times for three wins and two minors. Below best last time at this track (30.59) in a OPEN, finishing a 8 length fourth. Can hit the frame with the right run. PENNY DAZE (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Feisty Fawny (24.28) in a Grade 4. Has the pace to be prominent. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Leading player again. SUNTORY POPPY (3) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.
